ushinagar" title="Kushinagar">Kushinagar</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bodhi_tree" title="Bodhi tree" class="mw-redirect">Bodhi tree</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mahabodhi_Temple" title="Mahabodhi Temple">Mahabodhi Temple</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Abhijna" title="Abhijna">Higher Knowledge</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Iddhi" title="Iddhi">Supernormal Powers</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Miracles_of_Gautama_Buddha" title="Miracles of Gautama Buddha">Miracles of the Buddha</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Physical_characteristics_of_the_Buddha" title="Physical characteristics of the Buddha">Physical characteristics of the Buddha</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Family_of_Gautama_Buddha" title="Family of Gautama Buddha">Family of the Buddha</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Places_where_Gautama_Buddha_stayed" title="Places where Gautama Buddha stayed" class="mw-redirect">Places where Gautama Buddha stayed</a></div>
